Vehement/Sun Crusher/Reflector:



The Brotherhood Archbishop hovered several feet from the grass below him of 
South Africa.  He was only less than a mile away from the Cybertronian Fire.  
He didn't think there were any defenses left.  It would be safe, well, not 
safe, but easy to attack the base and not be badly damaged.

"Minions of the Chaos-Bringer, attack and test out your function on thy 
enemies!"
